{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/responsive-web-design-v9/workshop-registration-form/step-34","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"workshop-registration-form","demoType":null,"title":"Korak 34","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Funkcija <code>textarea</code> radi kao funkcija <code>input</code> tipa <code>text</code>, ali ima dodatnu prednost pri primanju višelinijskog teksta, zajedno sa početnim brojem linija i redovima teksta.</p>\n<p>Korisnici će moći da se registruju i kreiraju profil. Dodajte <code>label</code> sa tekstom <code>Provide a bio:</code> na kraju <code>fieldset</code>. Dodajte element <code>textarea</code> unutar elementa <code>label</code>. Zapamtite da <code>textarea</code> zahteva oznaku za zatvaranje (closing tag).</p>\n</section>","id":"60facde2d0dc61085b41063f","hasEditableBoundaries":true,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":0,"helpCategory":"HTML-CSS","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"responsive-web-design-v9","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":null,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/responsive-web-design-v9/workshop-registration-form/step-34"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":true,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"indexhtml","ext":"html","name":"index","contents":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n  <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n  <title>Registration Form</title>\n  <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"styles.css\" />\n</head>\n<body>\n  <h1>Registration Form</h1>\n  <p>Please fill out this form with the required information</p>\n  <form method=\"post\" action='https://register-demo.freecodecamp.org'>\n    <fieldset>\n      <label for=\"first-name\">Enter Your First Name: <input id=\"first-name\" type=\"text\" required /></label>\n      <label for=\"last-name\">Enter Your Last Name: <input id=\"last-name\" type=\"text\" required /></label>\n      <label for=\"email\">Enter Your Email: <input id=\"email\" type=\"email\" required /></label>\n      <label for=\"new-password\">Create a New Password: <input id=\"new-password\" type=\"password\" pattern=\"[a-z0-5]{8,}\" required /></label>\n    </fieldset>\n    <fieldset>\n      <legend>Account type (required)</legend>\n      <label for=\"personal-account\"><input id=\"personal-account\" type=\"radio\" name=\"account-type\" value=\"personal\" checked /> Personal</label>\n      <label for=\"business-account\"><input id=\"business-account\" type=\"radio\" name=\"account-type\" value=\"business\" /> Business</label>\n    </fieldset>\n    <fieldset>\n      <label>Upload a profile picture: <input type=\"file\" /></label>\n      <label>Input your age (years): <input type=\"number\" min=\"13\" max=\"120\" /></label>\n      <label>How did you hear about us?\n        <select>\n          <option value=\"\">(select one)</option>\n          <option value=\"1\">freeCodeCamp News</option>\n          <option value=\"2\">freeCodeCamp YouTube Channel</option>\n          <option value=\"3\">freeCodeCamp Forum</option>\n          <option value=\"4\">Other</option>\n        </select>\n      </label>\n      \n    </fieldset>\n    <a href=\"https://www.freecodecamp.org/news/terms-of-service\">Read our terms and conditions</a>\n    <label for=\"terms-and-conditions\">\n      <input id=\"terms-and-conditions\" type=\"checkbox\" required />\n      I accept the terms and conditions\n    </label>\n    <input type=\"submit\" value=\"Submit\" />\n  </form>\n</body>\n</html>","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[34,36],"history":["index.html"]},{"fileKey":"stylescss","ext":"css","name":"styles","contents":"body {\n  width: 100%;\n  height: 100vh;\n  margin: 0;\n  background-color: #1b1b32;\n  color: #f5f6f7;\n}\n\nlabel {\n  display: block;\n  margin: 0.5rem 0;\n}\n","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["styles.css"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Treba da dodate element za <code>label</code> na kraju trećeg <code>fie